com.spazedog.lib.rootfw3.extenders

Class BinaryExtender.Binary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.spazedog.lib.rootfw3.extenders.BinaryExtender.Binary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExtenderGroup
    Enclosing class:
    BinaryExtender

    public static class BinaryExtender.Binary
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExtenderGroup
    This class is used to handle binaries located in one of the $PATH variable directories.
    Note that this implements the ExtenderGroup interface, which means that it does not allow anything outside RootFW to create an instance of it. Use RootFW.binary(String) to retrieve an instance.
